Data Deletion and Privacy Rights
You have the right to request access to the personal data we hold about you, as well as request its correction or deletion. To submit a data deletion request, please contact us via email at:
Email:
jigsawpuzzlesforfree@outlook.com
When contacting us, please provide enough information for us to verify your identity and process your request.
Opt-Out Options
You can opt out of personalized ads through your device settings:
For iOS devices: Go to Settings > Privacy > Advertising and enable "Limit Ad Tracking."
Children's Privacy
Our app is not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children. If you believe a child has provided us with personal data, please contact us so we can delete the information.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with the updated effective date. Please review this policy periodically for any updates.
